letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518563\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.29508196721311475\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"976\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"976\" data-height=\"288\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"166\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f73e827f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9x45CIccckTy7l8n2yqjgKQ5anku58ibNmp4deSOY2l5tyL1Ubu4ibPia5CwCNhD8BtJKKSPlfxVyaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">3、语义聚类可视化揭示体素功能组织</span></span></h4>\n  <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 UMAP 可视化中，BraInCoRL 生成的体素权重呈现出清晰的语义聚类，人脸、场景、身体、食物等功能区域各自形成独立簇，且在多个被试间稳定复现。</span></span></h4>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518570\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7230464886251237\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1011\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1011\" data-height=\"731\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"406\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=26597458&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9x45CIccckTy7l8n2yqjgKml76ng43jtiaSkn36uFRydLQHIDb4sLnzLlicMcjRMwPIDymOAicwhwrw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">4、语义对齐与可解释性</span></span></h4>\n  <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过分析 BraInCoRL 的注意力机制，我们可以了解视觉皮层的功能组织，并发现与体素选择相关的图像。例如分析 Transformer 最后一层注意力权重，发现模型在预测“面孔区域”响应时，会自动关注上下文中的人脸图像，验证了其语义合理性。</span></span></h4>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518569\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.337037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1083\" data-height=\"365\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"189\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c48f1ee0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9x45CIccckTy7l8n2yqjgKiazEXnkIiaauwDmPRuIMskCz2msGp96090iawPLicSOE5KXqC8JspugROw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">5、自然语言驱动的大脑探查</span></span></h4>\n  <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">将 CLIP 文本提示（如 “a photo of a person's face”）映射为图像嵌入，输入 BraInCoRL，即可零样本预测整个皮层的激活图。</span></span></h4>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503518568\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42376237623762375\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1010\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1010\" data-height=\"428\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"238\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8a86bb61&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9x45CIccckTy7l8n2yqjgKPqfc0dpPpD38PhBqvj6QxFoWqCTSwt1u7VKfW7lgnD1fvdMF58dAibw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div>\n      <div>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">结语</span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">BraInCoRL 首次将上下文学习 (In-Context Learning) 引入计算神经科学，构建了一个无需微调、数据高效、可解释、支持语言交互的通用视觉皮层编码框架。该方法大幅降低了个体化脑编码模型的构建门槛，为未来在临床神经科学等数据受限场景中的应用开辟了新路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "BraInCoRL 模型首次将上下文元学习引入计算神经科学，实现无需微调即可高效、泛化地预测新被试的脑活动，大幅降低个体化脑编码模型构建门槛。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "BraInCoRL 模型首次将上下文元学习引入计算神经科学，实现无需微调即可高效、泛化地预测新被试的脑活动，大幅降低个体化脑编码模型构建门槛。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了 NeurIPS 2025 入选论文《Meta-Learning an In-Context Transformer Model of Human Higher Visual Cortex》，提出了一种名为 BraInCoRL 的脑编码模型。该模型旨在解决传统视觉编码模型对大量被试内数据依赖、成本高昂且难以推广的挑战。BraInCoRL 创新性地将元学习和上下文学习范式引入计算神经科学，将每个脑体素的视觉响应建模为一个独立的函数推断任务。通过 Transformer 架构，模型在训练阶段学习跨被试的视觉-神经映射共性，在测试阶段仅需少量（如 100 张）新被试的图像-脑响应对作为上下文，即可无需微调生成体素级编码器，准确预测其脑活动。实验结果表明，BraInCoRL 在数据效率、跨数据集泛化能力、语义聚类可视化、可解释性以及自然语言驱动的大脑探查方面均表现卓越，为临床神经科学等数据受限场景的应用开辟了新路径。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "BraInCoRL 首次将上下文学习引入计算神经科学，实现无需微调的跨被试脑活动预测。",
      "explanation": "模型通过元学习和上下文 Transformer，仅需少量示例数据即可为新被试生成专属编码器，无需传统方法的昂贵微调，极大提升了效率和可推广性。"
    },
